WEBVTT

01:43.009 --> 01:45.960
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.150 --> 01:49.110
[Episode 36]

01:55.500 --> 01:56.910
[Department of Anesthesiology]

02:02.710 --> 02:03.300
You're out.

02:03.330 --> 02:04.290
Have you been waiting long?

02:04.320 --> 02:04.820
No.

02:04.390 --> 02:06.780
[Department of Anesthesiology]

02:05.950 --> 02:07.060
It's snowing?

02:07.310 --> 02:07.910
Yes.

02:09.150 --> 02:09.669
Let's go.

02:18.829 --> 02:20.110
This is the first snow.

02:20.150 --> 02:20.970
Yeah.

02:21.030 --> 02:22.450
It's the first snow this year.

02:24.860 --> 02:26.030
It's so beautiful.

02:29.560 --> 02:31.750
I want to watch the snow.

02:32.920 --> 02:34.960
Then let me take you to a place,

02:35.710 --> 02:36.270
okay?

02:41.370 --> 02:42.870
Are you cold with the window open?

02:43.060 --> 02:44.400
I'm watching the snow.

03:07.110 --> 03:08.140
Are you cold?

03:10.560 --> 03:11.790
Come and warm your hands.

03:59.790 --> 04:01.050
Did you draw

04:01.490 --> 04:02.520
me?

04:03.570 --> 04:04.680
No.

04:04.870 --> 04:05.830
It's...

04:06.510 --> 04:07.550
a neighbor.

04:08.520 --> 04:09.530
Neighbor?

04:11.340 --> 04:11.980
Sure.

04:29.170 --> 04:30.630
Who did you draw?

04:32.790 --> 04:33.430
A doctor.

04:36.510 --> 04:38.060
Has something

04:38.240 --> 04:41.040
been troubling you lately?

04:42.260 --> 04:42.940
No.

04:44.980 --> 04:46.120
Just tell me

04:46.159 --> 04:47.700
if you have troubles.

04:47.790 --> 04:49.390
I'll share the burden with you.

04:51.000 --> 04:51.920
It's nothing.

04:51.990 --> 04:53.740
I've just been

04:53.770 --> 04:56.200
a bit busy with work, so I'm tired.

05:07.690 --> 05:10.030
I'm now

05:10.050 --> 05:11.810
your police station's...

05:12.000 --> 05:12.960
Director Xing.

05:14.470 --> 05:16.240
I have a few questions for you.

05:16.550 --> 05:19.620
Leniency for those who confess; severity for those who resist.

05:21.290 --> 05:22.580
What do you want to ask?

05:22.720 --> 05:23.860
Jiang Chengyi.

05:25.380 --> 05:27.190
On December 29

05:27.260 --> 05:28.830
of 2024...

05:32.530 --> 05:33.909
what's on your mind?

05:37.120 --> 05:38.210
Nothing.

05:39.360 --> 05:40.730
Answer me seriously.

05:40.880 --> 05:42.390
I'm asking you a question.

05:44.600 --> 05:45.750
On this day,

05:47.830 --> 05:49.600
I'm thinking that I have a girlfriend

05:50.550 --> 05:51.560
who's pretty,

05:51.750 --> 05:52.710
kind,

05:52.790 --> 05:53.600
earnest,

05:54.080 --> 05:55.580
and diligent at work.

05:56.470 --> 05:57.300
I think

05:58.590 --> 06:01.450
I'm very lucky to have met her.

06:01.750 --> 06:02.670
I feel blessed.

06:04.980 --> 06:07.020
You're suspected of excessive flattery.

06:07.050 --> 06:07.890
Answer it again.

06:14.680 --> 06:15.990
I'm thinking...

06:18.190 --> 06:19.990
After we got together,

06:20.370 --> 06:22.110
she encountered many changes

06:22.690 --> 06:23.860
and many troubles.

06:25.470 --> 06:26.430
But

06:28.060 --> 06:29.390
as a police officer

06:29.990 --> 06:31.350
and her boyfriend,

06:32.220 --> 06:34.080
I kept failing to protect her.

06:37.560 --> 06:38.370
It upsets me.

06:39.700 --> 06:40.470
I feel guilty.

06:42.270 --> 06:43.510
Do you have any evidence,

06:43.950 --> 06:45.930
or are you talking nonsense?

06:47.500 --> 06:49.600
These are all facts that happened.

06:50.900 --> 06:51.800
To me,

06:51.830 --> 06:52.980
that's not what happened.

06:53.190 --> 06:53.830
Overruled.

06:58.030 --> 06:58.860
Lu Yan.

06:59.430 --> 07:01.170
I said I’m Director Xing.

07:01.190 --> 07:02.370
Call me Director Xing.

07:02.980 --> 07:03.920
Director Xing...

07:03.950 --> 07:05.050
Jiang Chengyi.

07:06.190 --> 07:07.180
I'll ask you again.

07:07.650 --> 07:10.860
On December 29

07:11.930 --> 07:13.770
of 2014,

07:14.320 --> 07:15.400
what were you doing?

07:17.250 --> 07:19.600
Did you have an eye witness?

07:21.800 --> 07:23.040
That day,

07:23.670 --> 07:25.750
I was on the school field,

07:27.170 --> 07:29.420
and a girl ran into my embrace.

07:31.790 --> 07:33.850
The whole school was my witness.

07:38.800 --> 07:39.960
Shoot! Shoot!

07:40.070 --> 07:40.800
It's okay.

07:40.830 --> 07:42.020
Dear teachers

07:42.060 --> 07:43.030
and students,

07:43.070 --> 07:43.909
"The Sound of Ninghai"

07:43.950 --> 07:44.909
is back again.

07:44.930 --> 07:47.080
I'm Xiaoyou on duty today.

07:47.430 --> 07:49.330
I-I'm Lu Yan.

07:49.470 --> 07:50.350
May everyone

07:50.390 --> 07:52.200
who tunes in to our radio

07:52.230 --> 07:53.630
be blessed with good mood

07:53.630 --> 07:54.990
on this beautiful day

07:55.040 --> 07:55.510
to face

07:55.510 --> 07:56.990
today's work and study.

07:58.150 --> 08:00.360
Feel it with your heart.

08:00.510 --> 08:01.590
Lu Yan's impressive.

08:01.710 --> 08:02.670
Joining so many clubs

08:02.670 --> 08:04.200
in order to earn credits.

08:05.090 --> 08:08.260
[Ninghai University Radio Station]

08:05.230 --> 08:06.190
Let's move on to our

08:06.230 --> 08:07.070
fixed section,

08:07.070 --> 08:08.190
"I Want to Tell You."

08:08.540 --> 08:10.400
If any students or teachers want to

08:10.510 --> 08:11.510
submit their drafts,

08:11.550 --> 08:12.880
please feel free to approach us.

08:14.080 --> 08:19.280
[Ninghai University Radio Station]

08:14.390 --> 08:15.870
Lu Yan, who's beside me, seems to have

08:15.870 --> 08:16.750
something to say.

08:16.830 --> 08:18.430
Let's welcome Lu Yan.

08:22.380 --> 08:23.770
Jiang Chengyi.

08:24.160 --> 08:25.540
Are you listening?

08:27.530 --> 08:29.830
I want to request a song for you.

08:31.970 --> 08:33.070
I hope

08:33.309 --> 08:35.490
you'll remember our promise.

08:37.730 --> 08:39.280
I-I'll always be waiting for you.

08:42.270 --> 08:43.710
Props to Lu Yan.

08:43.740 --> 08:44.700
I have a girlfriend,

08:44.750 --> 08:45.690
but even I'm swooning.

08:45.780 --> 08:46.820
No, no.

08:46.990 --> 08:47.430
What promise?

08:47.430 --> 08:48.350
There's no promise.

08:48.350 --> 08:48.790
With whom?

08:48.810 --> 08:49.440
Nothing.

08:49.750 --> 08:50.830
Let's play ball. Stop talking.

08:50.830 --> 08:51.190
Go, go.

08:51.190 --> 08:52.270
Let's continue. Come on.

08:52.870 --> 08:53.990
Jiang's so lucky.

08:55.460 --> 08:56.480
[Ninghai University Radio Station]

08:58.070 --> 09:00.900
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

09:02.020 --> 09:04.590
♫Romance only exists with you♫

09:05.740 --> 09:07.630
♫Forever and ever into the future♫

09:08.540 --> 09:11.840
♫Let's be super sweet lovers♫

09:13.010 --> 09:15.540
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

09:16.630 --> 09:19.250
♫It's my privilege to make you happy♫

09:20.040 --> 09:22.270
♫Endless loving and longing♫

09:23.490 --> 09:30.560
♫Loving you, every day is Valentine's Day♫

09:43.610 --> 09:46.310
♫Holding hands while heading to the best outcome♫

09:45.880 --> 09:46.840
Hello?

09:46.940 --> 09:48.130
Is Jiang Chengyi here?

09:47.240 --> 09:50.200
♫Learning the beauty of waiting♫

09:48.220 --> 09:49.220
[Dormitory No. 8]

09:50.150 --> 09:51.780
He might be on his way.

09:55.620 --> 09:56.190
Yan!

09:56.940 --> 09:58.500
-Yan, are you okay?
-Are you okay?

09:58.590 --> 10:00.070
-Yan, come on.
-Are you okay?

10:00.090 --> 10:00.950
Is your foot okay?

10:00.990 --> 10:02.420
Watch where you're going!

10:03.290 --> 10:04.630
You bumped into her first!

10:04.660 --> 10:05.430
Apologize!

10:05.500 --> 10:06.420
Don't talk nonsense!

10:06.590 --> 10:07.380
It's okay, Man.

10:07.510 --> 10:09.270
We don't have time for you. Let's go.

10:10.310 --> 10:12.330
Come on. Let's go to the infirmary.

10:13.150 --> 10:13.990
Thank you.

10:24.430 --> 10:25.420
It's nothing.

10:25.550 --> 10:26.260
It's just

10:26.280 --> 10:28.260
a minor ankle injury.

10:28.290 --> 10:29.740
You'll be fine in a few days.

10:30.260 --> 10:31.130
Doctor.

10:31.190 --> 10:32.940
Can she still run?

10:33.110 --> 10:33.970
What?

10:34.030 --> 10:35.330
Of course not.

10:35.710 --> 10:36.310
Stay still.

10:36.430 --> 10:37.270
I'll get your medicine.

10:39.830 --> 10:41.600
If you're willing,

10:42.030 --> 10:42.950
wait for me at

10:43.590 --> 10:44.550
the 3,000-meter

10:45.630 --> 10:47.030
finish line at

10:48.230 --> 10:49.070
the sports meet.

10:52.510 --> 10:54.110
W-What are you doing?

10:56.760 --> 10:57.980
Where are you going?

10:59.840 --> 11:01.020
I'm going to the race.

11:04.230 --> 11:07.390
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:07.630 --> 11:09.910
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:10.190 --> 11:12.590
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:12.910 --> 11:15.190
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:15.430 --> 11:17.830
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:18.150 --> 11:20.750
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:21.030 --> 11:23.430
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:23.630 --> 11:26.230
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:26.880 --> 11:28.620
Why don't you talk her out of it?

11:28.720 --> 11:29.510
How can she run

11:29.540 --> 11:30.570
like this?

11:30.750 --> 11:31.190
Can't

11:31.190 --> 11:31.870
you see

11:31.870 --> 11:33.800
the stubborn look in her eyes?

11:33.830 --> 11:35.930
She might even cut ties with us.

11:36.390 --> 11:37.070
Forget it.

11:37.430 --> 11:38.640
Let her run.

11:38.870 --> 11:39.940
She needs closure.

11:39.990 --> 11:41.070
She'll regret not running.

11:41.590 --> 11:42.440
But Jiang Chengyi

11:42.470 --> 11:43.830
didn't even come.

11:44.070 --> 11:46.270
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:46.550 --> 11:49.350
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:49.590 --> 11:52.020
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:52.270 --> 11:54.390
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

11:54.510 --> 11:55.830
Lu Yan, come on!

11:58.630 --> 11:59.900
On your marks.

12:00.430 --> 12:03.030
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

12:03.190 --> 12:04.710
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

12:04.710 --> 12:05.830
Lu Yan, come on!

12:05.830 --> 12:07.670
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

12:08.030 --> 12:10.470
Go! Go, Lu Yan!

12:10.590 --> 12:13.190
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

12:13.360 --> 12:15.420
[Ninghai Engineering] [Ninghai Medicine]

12:17.500 --> 12:19.100
These freshmen are good.

12:22.750 --> 12:23.630
Defend!

12:23.650 --> 12:25.170
What's wrong? You're absent-minded.

12:25.510 --> 12:26.270
I'm sleepy.

12:27.270 --> 12:28.320
Jiang Chengyi,

12:28.350 --> 12:29.340
our captain.

12:29.440 --> 12:30.100
Shouldn't you

12:30.190 --> 12:31.520
check out our juniors?

12:35.540 --> 12:36.640
Nice shot!

12:36.950 --> 12:40.210
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

12:40.550 --> 12:43.500
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

12:43.790 --> 12:46.860
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

12:47.350 --> 12:49.580
-Go! Go! Go!
-Go! Go! Go!

12:49.750 --> 12:51.850
Her foot seems to be getting worse.

12:51.950 --> 12:52.570
Yeah.

12:52.630 --> 12:54.110
But there are so many rounds left.

13:01.820 --> 13:03.450
Lu Yan, come on!

13:03.630 --> 13:05.230
Lu Yan, come on!

13:05.390 --> 13:06.950
-Go! Go!
-Lu Yan!

13:33.600 --> 13:35.160
The race is near its end!

13:35.180 --> 13:36.750
There's one lap left!

13:37.050 --> 13:38.750
The runners are all sprinting!

13:38.780 --> 13:41.050
Runners, please keep going

13:41.070 --> 13:42.800
to achieve stellar results!

13:44.160 --> 13:45.870
If you're willing,

13:46.510 --> 13:47.670
wait for me at

13:48.130 --> 13:49.080
the 3,000-meter

13:49.510 --> 13:51.190
finish line at

13:51.700 --> 13:52.500
the sports meet.

13:53.250 --> 13:53.900
I’m leaving!

13:58.170 --> 13:59.220
♫As the city flickers♫

14:00.870 --> 14:03.370
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

14:02.410 --> 14:04.120
[Destined Champion]

14:04.920 --> 14:06.020
♫And you, who love to smile♫

14:06.580 --> 14:07.230
Lu Yan!

14:07.240 --> 14:09.490
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

14:08.070 --> 14:08.960
Are you okay?

14:08.980 --> 14:10.030
Yan, are you okay?

14:10.730 --> 14:12.790
♫The humor of time♫

14:10.830 --> 14:11.600
You're almost there.

14:11.670 --> 14:12.740
Can you go on?

14:14.560 --> 14:16.640
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

14:18.080 --> 14:23.470
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

14:25.220 --> 14:26.550
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

14:26.310 --> 14:28.710
Go! Go! Go!

14:27.950 --> 14:30.510
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

14:29.000 --> 14:31.630
Go! Go! Go!

14:31.870 --> 14:34.430
Go! Go! Go!

14:32.090 --> 14:33.290
♫The stubborn me♫

14:34.630 --> 14:37.230
Go! Go! Go!

14:34.750 --> 14:37.090
♫I always think of the far future♫

14:37.590 --> 14:40.740
Go! Go! Go!

14:38.240 --> 14:40.060
♫I walk willfully♫

14:40.910 --> 14:43.260
Go! Go! Go!

14:41.680 --> 14:44.220
♫Like a star revolving around♫

14:43.510 --> 14:46.070
Go! Go! Go!

14:45.240 --> 14:46.340
♫I turn around♫

14:46.440 --> 14:49.140
Go! Go! Go!

14:47.720 --> 14:50.990
♫But you're not behind me♫

14:52.880 --> 14:54.070
♫Losing you♫

14:55.290 --> 14:57.360
♫It's so unreal♫

14:58.660 --> 14:59.890
♫I hurt my love♫

15:00.800 --> 15:01.530
♫But still hope to♫

15:02.270 --> 15:04.990
♫Start anew♫

15:06.230 --> 15:08.250
♫There's a certain kind of squander♫

15:09.350 --> 15:11.200
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

15:12.520 --> 15:15.010
♫When you're not here♫

15:15.790 --> 15:18.900
♫Life becomes aimless♫

15:19.970 --> 15:21.220
♫I miss you♫

15:22.730 --> 15:24.550
♫It's so real♫

15:25.970 --> 15:27.310
♫The person I trust♫

15:28.080 --> 15:28.950
♫Insists on separating♫

15:29.710 --> 15:32.300
♫Who can explain?♫

15:33.860 --> 15:35.560
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

15:36.830 --> 15:38.700
♫I'm afraid you'll forget me♫

15:39.870 --> 15:42.300
♫To feel my heartache♫

15:41.480 --> 15:43.050
I thought you weren't coming.

15:43.280 --> 15:44.740
♫When I no longer have the best♫

15:44.260 --> 15:45.160
I'm here.

15:45.910 --> 15:49.330
♫I miss you missing me♫

16:01.390 --> 16:02.560
♫When I walk the path you've walked♫

16:03.410 --> 16:06.360
♫Waiting to bump into you on the street♫

16:07.930 --> 16:09.260
♫Like yesterday♫

16:10.350 --> 16:12.770
♫Our forever had no end♫

16:14.020 --> 16:14.990
♫I'm the stupid one♫

16:17.900 --> 16:20.300
♫You've already engraved yourself in my pulse♫

16:21.540 --> 16:22.680
Jiang Chengyi.

16:21.740 --> 16:27.240
♫I don't want you to disappear like a rainbow♫

16:23.900 --> 16:25.500
Whether it's

16:25.750 --> 16:26.550
the past

16:26.590 --> 16:27.670
or the future,

16:28.600 --> 16:30.550
like I did that day,

16:29.010 --> 16:30.170
♫Losing you♫

16:31.030 --> 16:32.830
I'll always run towards you.

16:31.300 --> 16:33.360
♫It's so unreal♫

16:34.710 --> 16:35.870
♫I hurt my love♫

16:35.920 --> 16:37.060
I don't think

16:36.400 --> 16:37.500
♫But still hope to♫

16:37.110 --> 16:38.030
there's anyone else

16:38.030 --> 16:39.430
as lucky as us

16:38.070 --> 16:41.010
♫Start anew♫

16:39.550 --> 16:41.180
to get a second chance.

16:42.070 --> 16:43.670
So this time,

16:42.290 --> 16:44.230
♫There's a certain kind of squander♫

16:44.680 --> 16:45.930
no matter what,

16:45.160 --> 16:47.250
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

16:46.220 --> 16:47.150
I'll always

16:47.150 --> 16:48.190
stay by your side.

16:49.040 --> 16:50.960
♫Losing you♫

16:51.660 --> 16:54.880
♫Life becomes aimless♫

16:52.190 --> 16:52.960
I know.

16:53.140 --> 16:54.810
I'll always be by your side too.

16:54.840 --> 16:55.880
Also,

16:55.910 --> 16:57.350
I realized that our story

16:56.040 --> 16:57.400
♫My love♫

16:57.370 --> 16:59.090
is always related to the snow.

16:58.670 --> 17:00.760
♫Must be honest♫

16:59.950 --> 17:00.670
So I prepared

17:00.700 --> 17:01.410
a small gift for you.

17:02.270 --> 17:03.540
♫The person I trust♫

17:03.910 --> 17:05.020
♫You are most deserving♫

17:05.500 --> 17:06.270
What do you think?

17:05.730 --> 17:08.640
♫Of good things♫

17:09.940 --> 17:11.619
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

17:11.800 --> 17:13.430
It can even spin.

17:12.900 --> 17:14.790
♫I'm afraid you'll forget me♫

17:15.140 --> 17:16.160
I'll put it on for you.

17:16.109 --> 17:18.530
♫To feel my heartache♫

17:19.400 --> 17:20.780
♫When I no longer have the best♫

17:21.579 --> 17:25.560
♫I miss you missing me♫

17:35.990 --> 17:36.550
Done.

17:36.590 --> 17:37.150
Do I look good?

17:38.720 --> 17:39.350
Yes.

17:39.410 --> 17:40.090
Yeah?

17:47.230 --> 17:47.990
From now on,

17:48.950 --> 17:49.990
on every snowy day,

17:50.790 --> 17:51.710
let's be together,

17:52.990 --> 17:53.640
okay?

17:55.990 --> 17:56.710
Okay?

19:41.170 --> 19:42.390
It's here.

19:42.950 --> 19:43.870
Thank you!

19:43.910 --> 19:44.590
Thank you!

19:44.670 --> 19:45.960
It smells so good.

19:46.020 --> 19:46.750
Honey.

19:47.070 --> 19:47.870
I'm starving.

20:00.640 --> 20:01.590
Honey.

20:02.470 --> 20:04.330
Even though you're pregnant,

20:04.630 --> 20:06.350
I can only bring you here to eat this.

20:07.150 --> 20:08.720
Don't you dare say that.

20:09.070 --> 20:10.640
I love noodles like this.

20:10.660 --> 20:11.750
I always came here

20:11.790 --> 20:13.400
with Lu Yan back in school.

20:13.630 --> 20:15.510
I even miss it every now and then.

20:15.970 --> 20:17.590
I know you're consoling me.

20:18.400 --> 20:19.840
The boss said he started

20:20.430 --> 20:20.950
running

20:20.950 --> 20:22.230
his stall a few days ago.

20:28.720 --> 20:29.640
Honey.

20:31.270 --> 20:33.660
Abalone and bird's nest is a meal.

20:34.100 --> 20:36.030
Noodles are also a meal.

20:36.710 --> 20:38.050
What matters is it's filling,

20:38.090 --> 20:38.940
don't you think?

20:43.000 --> 20:43.700
You should

20:43.830 --> 20:45.230
stop thinking about this.

20:46.030 --> 20:47.070
Most importantly,

20:47.470 --> 20:48.830
the matter has passed.

20:48.940 --> 20:49.870
What we should do now

20:49.870 --> 20:50.630
is to accept it

20:50.670 --> 20:51.730
and face the future.

20:56.350 --> 20:57.830
I even bought some hats just now.

20:57.950 --> 20:58.540
Look.

20:59.170 --> 21:00.240
One for you,

21:01.100 --> 21:02.030
one for me,

21:02.830 --> 21:04.080
and one for our baby.

21:05.150 --> 21:07.130
It's Chinese New Year. Let's have fun.

21:08.450 --> 21:09.220
Honey.

21:09.490 --> 21:10.720
I almost cost us our home.

21:10.750 --> 21:11.510
Should we—

21:11.660 --> 21:12.530
Zhong Wenxuan!

21:13.290 --> 21:14.600
This again?

21:15.580 --> 21:16.700
Sorry. I'm sorry.

21:17.020 --> 21:18.070
You're right, wifey.

21:18.590 --> 21:19.920
Get into the festive spirit.

21:20.190 --> 21:21.150
Exactly.

21:21.190 --> 21:22.150
Only by

21:22.150 --> 21:23.470
living well day by day

21:23.470 --> 21:24.910
can we have a bright future.

21:28.470 --> 21:29.270
Honey.

21:30.050 --> 21:31.400
Actually, I have a plan

21:32.070 --> 21:33.310
to discuss with you.

21:33.900 --> 21:34.460
Go ahead.

21:35.320 --> 21:36.590
Aren't short videos

21:36.590 --> 21:38.150
quite popular now?

21:38.510 --> 21:39.360
I want to write

21:39.390 --> 21:40.230
skits with Dalu.

21:40.860 --> 21:41.430
I'll find

21:41.430 --> 21:43.350
my old director

21:43.830 --> 21:45.000
and actor friends

21:45.020 --> 21:46.110
to help me build

21:46.750 --> 21:48.080
a video channel.

21:48.470 --> 21:49.550
Sure.

21:50.710 --> 21:52.450
Will you be a producer then?

21:53.050 --> 21:54.390
Producer Zhong.

21:54.470 --> 21:55.430
Can you give me a role

21:55.430 --> 21:56.860
when the script is done?

21:57.030 --> 21:58.850
My wife must be the leading actress.

21:58.880 --> 21:59.990
No thanks.

21:59.990 --> 22:00.630
It's too tiring.

22:00.670 --> 22:02.630
Just give me a supporting role.

22:04.220 --> 22:06.080
You can play whatever you want.

22:07.880 --> 22:08.670
Honey.

22:10.260 --> 22:11.230
Am I handsome?

22:12.110 --> 22:13.820
Yes, you are,

22:14.230 --> 22:16.030
but it's a bit loud.

22:16.110 --> 22:17.440
Why don't you take it off?

22:18.310 --> 22:19.290
Who cares?

22:19.590 --> 22:20.550
Then I'll put mine on too.

22:22.680 --> 22:25.120
Honey, I'm so lucky to have you.

22:27.760 --> 22:28.850
Honey!

22:28.900 --> 22:30.420
It's snowing!

22:30.610 --> 22:32.770
This is the first snow of the year, honey.

22:33.160 --> 22:35.060
It's so romantic!

22:42.290 --> 22:43.920
Take some photos for me!

22:53.650 --> 22:54.560
My wife's so beautiful.

22:54.590 --> 22:55.350
Come, let's take selfies too.

22:55.370 --> 22:55.810
Here.

23:52.240 --> 23:53.410
Why did you save me?

24:03.490 --> 24:04.850
It's my duty to save people.

24:06.200 --> 24:07.260
And you should be

24:07.310 --> 24:08.430
punished by the law.

24:12.850 --> 24:13.970
Don't you hate me?

24:15.350 --> 24:16.620
I hurt so many people;

24:17.680 --> 24:19.950
your colleagues, friends,

24:20.690 --> 24:22.190
and your future mother-in-law.

24:24.480 --> 24:25.680
So you know it yourself.

24:27.900 --> 24:28.990
I thought you were some

24:28.990 --> 24:30.300
extreme perverted killer.

24:32.940 --> 24:34.030
Tell me.

24:34.800 --> 24:36.360
You've done so many bad things

24:37.320 --> 24:38.390
and hurt so many people.

24:39.590 --> 24:40.630
Now that you're here,

24:41.010 --> 24:41.740
are you ashamed?

24:45.940 --> 24:47.250
In my life,

24:48.110 --> 24:49.240
nothing really

24:49.340 --> 24:50.310
belonged to me.

24:51.940 --> 24:53.200
But there is one thing

24:53.710 --> 24:54.550
where we're the same.

24:58.030 --> 24:59.510
We both want to get Lu Yan.

25:02.970 --> 25:03.940
You want

25:05.080 --> 25:06.650
to get Lu Yan.

25:09.670 --> 25:11.460
First of all, the word choice is problematic.

25:12.880 --> 25:15.510
You just want to coop Lu Yan up

25:15.610 --> 25:17.910
in your little world.

25:18.680 --> 25:20.490
Your so-called efforts

25:20.870 --> 25:21.590
and sacrifice

25:22.660 --> 25:24.040
were just

25:24.070 --> 25:25.940
to satisfy your selfish desires,

25:27.110 --> 25:27.630
