25:31.590 --> 25:32.590
That's your guess.

25:33.250 --> 25:34.280
Lu Yan doesn't think so.

25:38.570 --> 25:39.810
Still being stubborn?

25:41.550 --> 25:42.670
I hope that

25:43.450 --> 25:44.490
one day,

25:44.860 --> 25:46.530
you'll really figure out

25:47.160 --> 25:48.430
what you have done.

25:53.910 --> 25:55.150
If there's a chance,

25:57.880 --> 25:59.040
