27:32.650 --> 27:35.640
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

27:36.800 --> 27:38.390
♫The stubborn me♫

27:39.460 --> 27:42.160
♫I always think of the far future♫

27:42.940 --> 27:45.140
♫I walk willfully♫

27:43.270 --> 27:44.320
