27:59.990 --> 28:02.230
♫It's so unreal♫

28:03.370 --> 28:04.920
♫I hurt my love♫

28:05.510 --> 28:06.620
♫But still hope to♫

28:07.200 --> 28:10.000
♫Start anew♫

28:11.090 --> 28:13.260
♫There's a certain kind of squander♫

28:14.050 --> 28:16.380
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

28:17.740 --> 28:20.050
