28:34.410 --> 28:37.450
♫Who can explain?♫

28:38.570 --> 28:40.670
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

28:41.540 --> 28:43.800
♫I'm afraid you'll forget me♫

28:44.580 --> 28:47.330
♫To feel my heartache♫

28:47.990 --> 28:49.820
