34:03.660 --> 34:05.310
Is Sound ready?

34:06.350 --> 34:07.760
Is Lighting ready?

34:08.750 --> 34:10.639
Is Camera ready?

34:10.909 --> 34:11.699
Wei!

34:12.310 --> 34:13.380
Are you ready?

34:13.400 --> 34:14.050
Yes!

34:14.600 --> 34:16.340
Why isn't the actress here yet?

34:16.360 --> 34:17.030
Where's the actress?

34:17.060 --> 34:17.920
Coming!

34:17.949 --> 34:19.080
Coming, director.

34:19.100 --> 34:20.130
I'm ready.

34:20.270 --> 34:21.010
Honey.

34:21.480 --> 34:23.130
Can you work right after your birth?

34:23.270 --> 34:23.989
I'm fine.

34:24.730 --> 34:25.540
Honey.

34:25.710 --> 34:26.690
Your setting

34:26.790 --> 34:27.830
looks very professional.

34:27.850 --> 34:28.550
What do you think?

34:29.080 --> 34:30.159
I drew the background.

34:30.900 --> 34:32.340
I found the lights.

34:32.679 --> 34:34.420
I bought the props.

34:35.380 --> 34:36.070
Not bad, huh?

34:36.090 --> 34:36.719
Yeah.

34:36.800 --> 34:38.280
But your actress isn't doing too good.

34:38.300 --> 34:39.960
I'm so nervous for my first shoot.

34:40.310 --> 34:41.179
No, honey.

34:41.330 --> 34:42.710
It's hard to coordinate

34:42.730 --> 34:43.790
