34:51.120 --> 34:53.090
Honey, relax.

34:53.340 --> 34:54.500
Just remember that

34:54.750 --> 34:56.150
my name is Yin Tianchou,

34:56.510 --> 34:58.380
and you're Liu Piaopiao.

34:58.470 --> 34:59.640
I'll go get ready.

35:06.490 --> 35:07.510
Liu Piaopiao?

35:22.990 --> 35:24.190
Ms. Qiao Rui.

35:24.630 --> 35:26.260
Let's make an equivalent exchange.

35:27.010 --> 35:29.350
I'll give you half of my life,

35:30.000 --> 35:31.730
and you'll give me half of your life.

35:33.080 --> 35:35.590
Will you be my girlfriend?

35:42.730 --> 35:44.370
Thank you, Director Xing.

35:44.480 --> 35:45.360
It was a

35:45.400 --> 35:46.770
collective effort.

35:46.880 --> 35:48.130
By the way,

35:49.020 --> 35:50.310
since this case is closed,

35:50.450 --> 35:51.970
I'll be applying

35:52.040 --> 35:53.570
to go back to school and focus

35:53.630 --> 35:54.590
on my classes.

35:54.610 --> 35:55.620
Just to let you know.

35:55.170 --> 35:57.830
♫When we're hand in hand, even the equator possesses♫

35:57.550 --> 35:59.210
Okay, don't worry.

35:58.590 --> 36:01.620
♫Beauty like the aurora and white snow♫

36:02.770 --> 36:05.160
♫You close your eyes and make a wish, completely defenseless♫

36:04.850 --> 36:05.940
Okay, that's it then.

36:05.780 --> 36:08.740
♫I kiss your face secretly♫

36:05.970 --> 36:06.680
Goodbye.

36:10.110 --> 36:12.860
♫I long to hold your hands and weave beautiful dreams for you♫

36:13.690 --> 36:15.980
♫What we lack is not just time♫

36:17.890 --> 36:20.320
♫Losing sight of the world and our default end point♫

36:21.190 --> 36:23.560
♫As we write every page of our love by hand♫

36:24.270 --> 36:27.100
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

36:28.220 --> 36:30.790
♫Romance only exists with you♫

36:31.940 --> 36:33.830
♫Forever and ever into the future♫

36:34.740 --> 36:38.040
♫Let's be super sweet lovers♫

36:39.210 --> 36:41.740
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

36:42.830 --> 36:45.450
♫It's my privilege to make you happy♫

36:46.240 --> 36:48.470
♫Endless loving and longing♫

36:49.680 --> 36:55.920
♫Loving you, every day is Valentine's Day♫

36:54.840 --> 36:55.390
Hello.

36:55.390 --> 36:56.390
Can I take a photo with you?

36:56.420 --> 36:57.350
Sure, no problem.

37:03.300 --> 37:03.910
Sure.

37:03.990 --> 37:04.970
Me too. Thank you.

37:05.570 --> 37:06.480
And us.

37:08.780 --> 37:09.490
Bye.

37:11.630 --> 37:12.600
I didn't expect you

37:12.630 --> 37:13.550
to sing so well.

37:23.190 --> 37:25.140
Actually, I've always liked singing.

37:25.570 --> 37:26.430
But they thought

37:26.450 --> 37:28.010
I don't sound good,

37:28.100 --> 37:29.290
so I wasn't allowed to sing.

37:28.410 --> 37:31.810
♫Charging into the world, with you in my backseat♫

37:32.230 --> 37:33.900
Then right now,

37:33.420 --> 37:36.770
♫Pretending not to care even though you're all I care about♫

37:33.930 --> 37:36.070
you're a superstar singing on the street?

37:36.230 --> 37:37.500
Aren't you worried the media

37:37.520 --> 37:38.660
