37:38.610 --> 37:42.030
♫I couldn't tell you for some unknown reason♫

37:38.910 --> 37:40.160
What's there to worry about?

37:40.880 --> 37:42.040
I'm no longer that

37:42.060 --> 37:42.900
superstar I was.

37:43.210 --> 37:48.270
♫That I like you the way you are♫

37:43.250 --> 37:44.430
Now,

37:45.140 --> 37:45.910
I do what

37:45.910 --> 37:46.990
I want to every day.

37:47.580 --> 37:48.890
I just be myself.

37:49.090 --> 37:53.460
♫Like raindrops falling, wishing to return to the sky♫

37:51.830 --> 37:52.670
That's nice.

37:54.150 --> 37:54.750
Congrats.

37:54.250 --> 37:58.660
♫As long as I can meet you, I'd gladly endure anything♫

37:59.180 --> 38:03.710
♫Like a shadow quietly guarding its light source♫

38:00.380 --> 38:02.050
Have you been singing here lately?

38:03.030 --> 38:04.390
You chose a good spot.

38:04.430 --> 38:08.680
♫You keep walking, and I'll walk with you forever♫

38:05.250 --> 38:06.830
That is our university.

38:07.310 --> 38:08.960
There are many high schools nearby.

38:09.370 --> 38:10.240
I bet you'd

38:09.800 --> 38:14.510
♫You're the shooting star I chase with all my might♫

38:10.270 --> 38:11.550
gain many fans.

38:13.240 --> 38:14.920
I chose this spot on purpose.

38:15.750 --> 38:20.180
♫I can't hold you, but I can still make a wish♫

38:18.280 --> 38:19.530
Because I can...

38:20.750 --> 38:24.780
♫So precious, so bittersweet♫

38:20.800 --> 38:22.050
run into you.

38:25.760 --> 38:27.030
I've been waiting for today.

38:26.560 --> 38:30.610
♫Even the wind knows the one I love is you♫

38:29.750 --> 38:31.620
I've been waiting to meet you again.

38:31.290 --> 38:35.330
♫You are the shooting star I gaze at and chase♫

38:34.910 --> 38:36.740
Let me introduce myself again.

38:37.230 --> 38:41.440
♫You saved my lonely heart♫

38:38.120 --> 38:39.280
I'm Yu Bofeng.

38:39.300 --> 38:40.870
I'm 23 years old.

38:41.220 --> 38:42.520
I'm 1.88 meters tall.

38:42.350 --> 38:46.270
♫I'm so lucky to have fallen for you♫

38:43.200 --> 38:44.390
I don't have a stable job

38:44.420 --> 38:45.410
right now.

38:47.530 --> 38:50.910
♫I wish, at the edge of my world♫

38:48.030 --> 38:49.750
My future's uncertain too.

38:51.680 --> 38:53.550
But there's one thing I'm sure of.

38:52.700 --> 38:56.260
♫You'd fall in love with me too♫

38:56.780 --> 38:58.230
From now on,

38:58.250 --> 38:59.730
