39:02.240 --> 39:04.040
I want to be with you,

39:05.590 --> 39:06.620
never leaving you.

39:10.360 --> 39:11.970
Can you give me a chance?

39:14.740 --> 39:16.010
I want to be with you.

39:17.950 --> 39:21.940
♫The streetlight watches you leave♫

39:23.420 --> 39:27.710
♫These hands can't yet hold onto love♫

39:28.620 --> 39:29.830
Wait.

39:28.820 --> 39:32.130
♫I don't want to miss any of your tearful or joyful moments♫

39:30.280 --> 39:31.350
Did I...

39:31.420 --> 39:31.900
I...

39:33.770 --> 39:38.320
♫That I like you the way you are♫

39:38.710 --> 39:43.300
♫Like raindrops falling, wishing to return to the sky♫

39:44.230 --> 39:48.390
♫As long as I can meet you, I'd gladly endure anything♫

39:49.340 --> 39:53.590
♫Like a shadow quietly guarding its light source♫

39:54.130 --> 39:58.490
♫You keep walking, and I'll walk with you forever♫

39:59.500 --> 40:04.240
♫You're the shooting star I chase with all my might♫

40:05.120 --> 40:09.260
♫You saved my lonely heart♫

40:10.830 --> 40:14.720
♫I'm so lucky to have fallen for you♫

40:16.120 --> 40:19.210
♫I wish, at the edge of my world♫

40:20.870 --> 40:23.290
♫You'd fall in love with me too♫

40:22.400 --> 40:31.120
[Qianya Tourism]

40:22.800 --> 40:24.470
Are you two going on a honeymoon trip?

40:24.730 --> 40:26.080
I recommend the Maldives.

40:26.990 --> 40:28.380
Overseas might be tough.

40:28.400 --> 40:29.850
Any local plans?

40:30.040 --> 40:31.100
Locally,

40:31.190 --> 40:32.230
you can go skiing in Xinjiang

40:32.270 --> 40:33.550
or go to Hainan

40:33.570 --> 40:34.520
to swim.

40:34.550 --> 40:36.110
Dali, Yunnan is a great choice too.

40:36.920 --> 40:38.890
How long does it take to make all the stops?

40:39.220 --> 40:40.260
At least a dozen days.

40:40.290 --> 40:41.370
Isn't this a honeymoon trip?

40:41.390 --> 40:42.640
You should enjoy it to the fullest.

40:42.810 --> 40:45.080
I don't think I can do a dozen days.

40:45.100 --> 40:46.390
How many leave days do you have?

40:46.520 --> 40:48.350
About four or five days.

40:49.200 --> 40:50.640
What about shorter trips?

40:51.120 --> 40:52.070
We have them too.

40:52.090 --> 40:52.750
Take a look.

40:52.810 --> 40:53.870
These are our top

40:53.870 --> 40:54.660
recommendations.

40:55.870 --> 40:56.880
What do you think?

40:59.230 --> 41:00.420
Guizhou.

41:01.180 --> 41:02.190
Sichuan.

41:03.630 --> 41:04.840
Sichuan–Tibet Route.

41:05.260 --> 41:06.340
This is too far.

41:06.770 --> 41:07.790
We need to drive.

41:07.830 --> 41:08.670
Sanxingdui.

41:09.710 --> 41:10.800
Choose one.

41:11.260 --> 41:12.100
Anyway,

41:12.430 --> 41:13.470
if it's with you,

41:13.470 --> 41:14.150
anywhere's good.

41:17.630 --> 41:19.250
We'll think about it first.

41:19.650 --> 41:20.890
-Okay.
-Thank you.

41:21.070 --> 41:21.690
Let's go.

41:21.940 --> 41:22.460
Let's go.

41:22.480 --> 41:23.110
Go?

41:23.560 --> 41:24.430
Let's consider first.

41:26.890 --> 41:27.880
Where do you think

41:27.880 --> 41:29.110
we should go?

41:28.700 --> 41:33.530
[Shangqiu Road]

41:29.150 --> 41:31.040
Yunnan or...

41:31.320 --> 41:32.630
skiing in Altay?

41:32.870 --> 41:34.080
I only have a few days off.

41:34.130 --> 41:35.450
How can we go to so many places?

41:36.150 --> 41:38.080
Don't you have five days next year?

41:38.140 --> 41:39.180
And five days after that.

41:39.210 --> 41:40.300
And five days the year after.

41:40.320 --> 41:41.580
Five days every year.

41:41.600 --> 41:43.700
Then let's go to one place a year.

41:44.400 --> 41:44.830
Okay?

41:45.060 --> 41:45.690
Okay.

41:46.040 --> 41:47.250
Our annual trip.

41:49.800 --> 41:51.070
Robbery!

41:51.110 --> 41:51.950
Robbery!

41:53.030 --> 41:54.520
Robbery in this age?

41:54.540 --> 41:55.480
Captain Jiang.

41:55.740 --> 41:56.180
Go!

41:56.480 --> 41:57.090
Let's go!

42:27.990 --> 42:29.030
I'm Yin Tianchou.

42:29.050 --> 42:29.790
And you are?

42:29.820 --> 42:31.020
I'm Liu Piaopiao.

42:31.050 --> 42:32.480
What do you want to discuss with me?

42:32.510 --> 42:34.060
How to ask my boss for a pay raise.

42:34.200 --> 42:35.840
For a pay raise,

42:35.860 --> 42:37.890
start with the basics.

42:37.920 --> 42:38.790
You can treat me

42:38.830 --> 42:39.670
as your boss

42:39.690 --> 42:40.850
and make your request.

42:41.090 --> 42:43.470
Boss, raise my pay.

42:43.550 --> 42:44.930
Watch your tone.

42:44.960 --> 42:46.380
I'm your boss now.

42:46.400 --> 42:47.650
You're my subordinate.

42:47.670 --> 42:49.430
You must watch your tone.

42:47.750 --> 42:50.400
♫When we're hand in hand, even the equator possesses♫

42:49.480 --> 42:50.920
Try starting with a greeting.

42:50.940 --> 42:52.160
Say, "Good morning, sir,"

42:51.170 --> 42:54.190
♫Beauty like the aurora and white snow♫

42:52.180 --> 42:54.590
or "Morning, boss."

42:54.610 --> 42:56.260
Morning, boss.

42:55.350 --> 42:57.730
♫You close your eyes and make a wish, completely defenseless♫

42:56.590 --> 42:58.620
Use a gentle tone.

42:58.350 --> 43:01.310
♫I kiss your face secretly♫

42:59.120 --> 43:01.260
You can try lowering your head...

43:02.690 --> 43:05.440
♫I long to hold your hands and weave beautiful dreams for you♫

43:03.090 --> 43:05.930
and wait for the other person to speak before looking up.

43:06.270 --> 43:08.520
♫What we lack is not just time♫

43:06.330 --> 43:07.330
What is it?

43:08.290 --> 43:09.860
Morning, boss.

43:10.060 --> 43:11.810
Your eyes are too dead.

43:10.470 --> 43:12.890
♫Losing sight of the world and our default end point♫

43:11.880 --> 43:14.030
Look more alive.

43:13.760 --> 43:16.140
♫As we write every page of our love by hand♫

43:14.100 --> 43:14.830
Again.

43:15.150 --> 43:16.600
Morning, boss.

43:16.630 --> 43:18.080
It's too much.

43:16.840 --> 43:19.350
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

43:18.440 --> 43:19.280
Be more earnest.

43:19.470 --> 43:20.240
Again.

43:20.730 --> 43:22.250
Morning, boss.

43:20.800 --> 43:23.210
♫Romance only exists with you♫

43:22.270 --> 43:23.940
That's a death stare.

43:23.950 --> 43:25.310
Are you trying to scare the boss?

43:24.520 --> 43:26.320
♫Forever and ever into the future♫

43:25.880 --> 43:26.710
Be natural.

43:27.320 --> 43:30.940
♫Let's be super sweet lovers♫

43:29.040 --> 43:29.820
Again.

43:30.830 --> 43:32.660
Morning, boss.

43:31.780 --> 43:34.310
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

43:34.140 --> 43:35.140
Bravo!

43:35.400 --> 43:37.920
♫It's my privilege to make you happy♫

43:35.450 --> 43:37.020
Maintain this state.

43:37.190 --> 43:37.990
Be smart with

43:37.990 --> 43:39.200
your phrasing.

43:38.820 --> 43:41.110
♫Endless loving and longing♫

43:39.220 --> 43:40.630
Don't ever mention money.

43:40.710 --> 43:41.860
Tell them how much

43:41.890 --> 43:43.130
you've contributed,

43:42.260 --> 43:48.460
♫Loving you, every day is Valentine's Day♫

43:43.150 --> 43:44.830
and a raise is the recognition you need

43:44.870 --> 43:45.800
and a representation

43:45.830 --> 43:48.200
of your personal value.

43:51.340 --> 43:53.660
Boss, raise my pay.

43:58.000 --> 43:59.010
Honey! Honey!

43:59.040 --> 44:00.720
Honey, look!

44:00.750 --> 44:01.560
What's wrong?

44:01.590 --> 44:02.830
There are so many

44:02.880 --> 44:04.620
likes and comments on our video.

44:05.920 --> 44:07.040
Wow, it's real.

44:07.110 --> 44:08.680
[Comments] [Likes] [Saves]

44:07.330 --> 44:08.820
There are so many!

44:08.870 --> 44:09.460
Just now,

44:09.460 --> 44:10.590
a few businesses

44:10.620 --> 44:12.140
contacted me about live commerce.

44:12.160 --> 44:12.780
I did it

44:12.800 --> 44:13.950
just for fun,

44:13.970 --> 44:15.130
but people actually watched it?

44:15.320 --> 44:15.970
Honey.

44:16.520 --> 44:17.460
You're popular.

44:18.950 --> 44:20.150
What should we do?

44:20.230 --> 44:22.480
Don't worry. I'm ready.

44:22.510 --> 44:23.350
Here.

44:23.910 --> 44:24.920
Honey.

44:25.610 --> 44:26.900
What are all these?

44:26.920 --> 44:28.120
Scripts.

44:28.270 --> 44:29.390
Scripts?

44:29.890 --> 44:30.830
I've thought about it.

44:30.860 --> 44:31.630
If we're serious,

44:31.630 --> 44:32.660
let's do it well.

44:32.680 --> 44:33.650
Let's shoot a series.

44:33.710 --> 44:34.670
I'll get my staff

44:34.710 --> 44:36.440
to help with the shoot tomorrow.

44:37.380 --> 44:38.640
I agree.

44:38.680 --> 44:39.710
Let's focus on

44:39.710 --> 44:40.760
developing the content.

44:40.780 --> 44:42.500
We'll think about commerce later.

44:42.710 --> 44:43.850
Thank you for your support.

44:43.880 --> 44:45.080
Let me see...

44:46.400 --> 44:48.810
"Love Is Sweet"?

44:48.920 --> 44:51.340
Sweet romance is all the rage.

44:52.910 --> 44:54.530
"Follow Your Heart"?

44:54.550 --> 44:57.050
Intriguing historical mystery.

44:59.290 --> 45:00.420
"Love Song in Winter"?

45:00.740 --> 45:01.270
Honey.

45:01.270 --> 45:02.650
You know this script?

45:03.150 --> 45:03.990
No, I don't.

45:03.990 --> 45:04.550
But I know

45:04.570 --> 45:06.160
we eat dumplings in winter.

45:06.280 --> 45:07.980
Suspense romance.

45:08.350 --> 45:09.660
Guaranteed hit.

45:10.830 --> 45:13.200
-Guaranteed hit!
-Guaranteed hit!
